§2§lWhat is a greg pack:

§0§0§a§8§6§7§fGregtech is a mod that its goal is to automate everything posible and as you think a greg pack is a modpack made with this mod. In general the goal of those packs is to get some item or liquid using automation, this mods is a little more complex and needs patience but the quest book will try to guide you.

§2§5§lOther things:

§f§l§l§rThe modpack progression is focused on GTCE Unoffical mod, is the mod that this modpack uses as a principal there are some things new like the terminal and glowing machines 
But is almost the same thing as normal greg
The terminal is a machine that you spawned with, needs some parts before you call fully use it but for now it can be use to tell the state of some machines/multiblocks and there is some recepie graphs and also some nice games.
(The modpack introduction may change)
§1§2§3§4§3§b§lHave fun :D
Welcome to the world

§6§lGregTech Tools
§f
In GregTech there are custom tools like pickaxes, axes and mining hammer, that can be made out almost every material.

Even though there is no vein miner, GregTech Axes include a build-in timber fonctionality.

§3§4§5§6§7§9§a§b§lHammer:§r§2§3§4§4§k§f A crafting tool used to for a lot of early game recipes. It also works as a mining tool for ores to crush them.

§9§l§b§lFile:§r A crafting tool, used to make rods.

§b§lWire Cutter:§r A crafting tool. It is needed to connect wires together. Right-clicking on wires will enable or disable connection to other blocks.

§9§l§b§lSaw:§r Another crafting tool. the tool isn't needed that often but you can still use it to get §a6§f Planks per Log§r.

§f§l§b§lMortar:§r A crafting tool, to grind various things into dust form.

§b§lWrench:§r A crafting tool. But also a mining tool for GregTech machines. It also has right click functions to double as a Forge §6Wrench for other mods§r. Right Click also allows you to set the output side of GregTech machines. Shift right clicking allows you to rotate GregTech machines.
Wrought Iron can be made, early on in a furnace by smelting iron nuggets.

§l§2§b§lGregTech Ore Veins

§fIn Gregtech CEu the ores have a different generation from the vanila minecraft.
They generate in large veins that have 106 ores and usually they are 3 chunks apart from each other and have 3-4 different ores inside them. 
Its a mess in the start to find some ores that you need but it will become more easy as you progress. 


The deep dark is a mining dimension that you unlock in MV tier where you can find all the Gregtech ores, the best way is to just put some one block or multiblock miners and let them work
But remember to load the chunks before leaving to do other things

§b§lSoft Mallet:§r A tool to pause machines from working with right-click. Right-clicking again resumes working. 

§b§lKnife:§r A mediocre weapon, but also, a crafting tool!

§b§lScrewdriver:§r A crafting tool. It is used for special configuration of machines and Covers.

§b§lCrowbar:§r A niche tool to remove Covers from GregTech machines with a right-click.

Craft a petal apothecary and expolre the world of botania.

Fill the apothecary with water, drop the crafting materials inside it and drop 1 seed to finish the recipe.

Place blocks around the pure daisy, after a bit of time they will change into another form.

You can check jei for the recipes.

By shift+right clicking an endoflame while using the bind mode on the wand of the forest, and then right clicking a mana spreader and using that same technique you can bind the spreader to a mana pool which will slowly fill it up if §bmana§f is produced by the flower.
The living alloy is a material made from iron dust and living mixture which is used in the crafting of the first 2 gregtech multiblocks.

The endoflame consumes any fuel dropped in a 7×7×7 area around it, then produces 3 §bMana§f every 2 ticks for half of the fuel's burn time. For example, Charcoal is burned for 800 ticks (40 seconds), producing 1200 §bMana§f.
Livingrock is one of the materials mad ewith the pure daisy

The Mana Pool can be used as a mana buffer, or if enough mana is inside it you can drop
an item in it to infuse it with mana.
The Living mixture is a mix between crushed livingrock and livingwood pulp.
You need §4§l348 Living Mixture §ffor the coke oven. That's §7§6174 Livingwood and Livingrock each§f.

§rThe §6primitive blast furnace (PBF)§f, takes coal, coal coke or charcoal and turns iron or wrought iron into §7steel, §fdepending on the materials you use the time it takes to produce steel changes with the lowest being coal coke and wrought iron with 30 sec. per steel.

This is your last huge multiblock in the §d§9§bBotanical Age§f. But it takes §4§l132 Firebricks. That's 132 Livingalloy and 132 Living mixture.

§fGood Luck!
Steel is used to make Manasteel
§b§fWith§b manasteel§f you can start your journey into the world of Gregtech CEu.
